# Comprehensive Verification Guidelines

## Verification Checklist
- Test all code changes across multiple environments
- Verify API endpoints and data flows end-to-end
- Check integration points and dependencies
- Validate error handling and edge cases

## Environment Testing
- Local development environment verification
- Staging/preview environment testing
- Production environment validation
- Cross-browser and device compatibility

## Quality Assurance
- Run full test suite before deployment
- Perform manual testing of critical paths
- Verify performance and security aspects
- Check accessibility and user experience

## Documentation and Communication
- Update documentation for any changes
- Communicate breaking changes clearly
- Provide migration guides when necessary
- Ensure team alignment on verification processes